      "raw_text": "HOMESEEKERS, ATTENTION!\n\n\nThe Flathead reservation Is soon\nto be opened to settlers. Richest\nsoil in United States and a home\nstead will be worth 5000 per acre.\nFine climate. We show how to Sc.\ncure \"a home for you and a for.\ntune too\" Join our club. Mem\nbership fee is only $40. For all\nmaps, charts and complete informal\nton up to and even after the open\ning. If you are a poor man or wo-\nman and want to better yerr con-\ndition see us about this. Call or\nwrite. Empire Realty Co., state\nagents, 2O7-2OS Mohawk block. IA"
